TL;DR Hey, I&rsquo;m Thwani Sithole. I am a software developer, and I am interested in anything &lsquo;JavaScript&rsquo;
About I am a developer based in Durban, South Africa. I hold a Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Applied Mathematics and an Honours degree in Computer Science, both from the University of the Witwatersrand.
I currently work as a C# developer, with most of my work focused on web APIs and SQL Server. My interests, however, lie in JavaScript.
